 better.<br>Save all of your Light Stones and Greater Light Stones, and do the light stone quest.<br>Every Greater Light Stone is worth about 7 - 9 plat per stone.<br><br>You will also get exp. from turning in the stones.<br><br>Since I am very close to your level, feel free to email me with anny questions, I would be happy to assist you with areas to fight.<br><br>I am still learning what spell order will work for my style, so I do not have the best info in that field.<br>But I can defintely advise you on the safer areas to level.<br>And what to fight to get the most exp. per kill.<br><br><br>If you are on the Rathe Server, send me a tell.<br><br>Zoidicus (Guardians of the Faith) Rathe server<br></p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
